Honor Harger has lectured extensively and spoken publicly on her work in a variety of forums.
Harger was the guest curator for the Transmediale festival in Berlin in 2010.
After relocating to Europe in 1999, Harger undertook projects with the Bauhaus Dessau Foundation in Germany, the publishing house Arkzin in Croatia, and the Kiasma contemporary art museum in Finland.
